dict.string: The path to the matlab executable on your system (change this to be correct0 Don't mess with this This is the datatask file that contains the input information Extract the data out of the datatask file in the form of a 3d path series The resolution parameter - higher value will lead to a partition into smaller communities. The temporal parameter - higher value will lead to nodes more likely to stay in same cluster This module converts the 3d path series to a 3d point series Convert the input times into time bins This module converts the 3d point series data into a (dense) weighted adjacency matrix
